      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "  Fixes frontmatter title handling.\r\n\r\n  - Blank title values, such as `title:` or `title: null`, now publish as no title.\r\n  - Omitted `title` still falls back to the note filename.\r\n  - Non-string title values are now converted predictably:\r\n    - numbers/booleans become strings\r\n    - arrays and objects are serialized as JSON-style strings\r\n  - Added tests for title normalization edge cases.\r\n  \r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/lylo/obsidian-pagecord/compare/1.0.3...1.0.4",
